Introduction

The EthFw package consists of firmware for Ethernet switch, profiling tools and demos/applications for Jacinto 7 family of devices

Licensing

Refer to EthFw manifest [HTML].

Getting Started

The EthFw User Guide [HTML] provides the documentation and references necessary to begin development on Ethernet Switch in TI's Jacinto 7 Family of devices using EthFw.
